        "gg35OU3qs2i_text": "<p>All Omnis creams are <strong>Made in Italy,</strong> produced by a<strong> small family owned</strong> <strong>lab with 38 years of experience.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>❌ You won’t find: silicones, parabens, alcohol, synthetic fragrances. And of course, we do NOT test on animals!</p>"
